## Requirements

- Python 3.8+
- [Ollama](https://ollama.com/download) installed and running
- Mistral model pulled via Ollama

## Installation

1. **Install Ollama** (if not already):
   [https://ollama.com/download](https://ollama.com/download)

2. **Pull the Mistral model:**

```bash
ollama pull mistral
